[Declarer "W"]
[Contract "7NT"]
[Vulnerable "All"]
[Student "S"]
[Deal "E:J952.AJ743.AQ.98 8.986.T984.QT752 AKQ643.K5.K73.AK T7.QT2.J652.J643"]
[Auction "E"]
1H pass 2S pass 3S pass 4NT pass 5H pass 7NT pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{WEST has a powerhouse and knows she will reach a slam somewhere. When EAST

supports the ♠s, it seems she has found her spot.

Blackwood tells her that EAST has two Aces.

She can see there are 12 tricks available and decides to take a chance that

EAST will have a thirteenth trick somewhere among his opening hand points.

She bids 7NT.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: W, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:3, nBasis: 0, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]

